OL,3,CGovernment backed local inquiries into
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs to be announced
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary will announce a
OL,7,Fplan for government-backed local
OL,8,Finquiries into grooming gangs, some
OL,9,FLabour MPs have been told.
OL,11,FITV News understands Home Secretary
OL,12,FYvette Cooper will make the
OL,13,Fannouncement this afternoon in
OL,14,Fresponse to calls for a national
OL,15,Finquiry into the scandal from the
OL,16,FConservatives, Reform UK, and some
OL,17,FLabour MPs.
