OL,3,CGovernment backed local inquiries into
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs to be announced
OL,6,FCooper is also expected to announce
OL,7,Fnew directions to police forces on
OL,8,Finvestigating cases of child sexual
OL,9,Fexploitation.
OL,11,FThe move comes after three Labour MPs
OL,12,Fpublicly expressed support for a
OL,13,Fnational inquiry - Liverpool Walton MP
OL,14,FDan Carden, Rotherham MP Sarah
OL,15,FChampion, and Rochdale MP Paul Waugh.
OL,17,FOther senior Labour figures - Andy
OL,18,FBurnham and former MP Harriet Harman -
OL,19,Falso joined the calls, saying they
OL,20,Fwould support a limited new inquiry.
