OL,3,CGovernment backed local inquiries into
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs to be announced
OL,6,FThe Rotherham MP has campaigned
OL,7,Ftirelessly to tackle child sexual
OL,8,Fexploitation and violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls throughout her career
OL,10,Fin politics.
OL,12,FThe government had so far resisted
OL,13,Fcalls from the Conservatives, Reform,
OL,14,Fand their own MPs to hold a national
OL,15,Finquiry, arguing a new inquiry would
OL,16,Fdelay implementing the recommendations
OL,17,Ffrom a 2022 inquiry into child sexual
OL,18,Fexploitation.
