OL,3,CGovernment backed local inquiries into
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs to be announced
OL,6,FThe head of that inquiry argued
OL,7,Fherself any new probe could delay
OL,8,Faction on tackling the problem. Alexis
OL,9,FJay and others suggest council-led
OL,10,Finquiries are more effective and can
OL,11,Fdeliver action faster.
OL,13,FThe seven-year Jay inquiry said child
OL,14,Fsexual abuse was "endemic" in England
OL,15,Fand Wales, calling for "urgent" action
OL,16,Ffrom the government.
