OL,3,CGovernment backed local inquiries into
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs to be announced
OL,6,FThe debate around tackling grooming
OL,7,Fgangs was thrust to the front of the
OL,8,Fnews agenda last week after tech
OL,9,Fbillionaire and X owner Elon Musk
OL,10,Fbegan attacking Sir Keir Starmer and
OL,11,Fhis government, accusing them of being
OL,12,F"complicit" in the scandal.
OL,14,FThe Conservatives and Reform responded
OL,15,Fto Musk's outbursts by calling for a
OL,16,Fnational inquiry, which he then also
OL,17,Fexpressed support for.
