OL,6,FIn light of the mounting debate around
OL,7,Fthe grooming gangs scandal, the
OL,8,Fgovernment acted on one of the
OL,9,Frecommendations from the Jay report -
OL,10,Fintroducing criminal sanctions for
OL,11,Fprofessionals who work with children
OL,12,Fif they fail to report claims of child
OL,13,Fsexual abuse.
